被取消的《Rebel Moon》游戏开发商起诉 Netflix https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/developer-of-cancelled-rebel-moon-game-sues-netflix-3506051?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=developer-of-cancelled-rebel-moon-游戏起诉 NetflixImogen Donovan Thu, 28 Sep 2023 16:31:50 +0000 Film NewsGaming NewsNewsTabletop Gaming https://www.nme.com/?p=3506051 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>诉讼中写道：“斯奈德先生明确要求制作一款基于《Rebel Moon》的 TTRPG”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/developer-of-cancelled-rebel-moon-game-sues-netflix-3506051">被取消的《Rebel Moon》游戏开发商起诉 Netflix 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rebel-moon-ttrpg-developer-suing-netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Evil Genius Games 已对<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a>采取法律行动，指控其“错误终止”一份以<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/rebel-moon"><em>Rebel Moon</em></a>世界为背景的桌面角色扮演游戏开发合同。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-inon-zur-starfield-score-3500117">伊农·祖尔 (Inon Zur) 如何创造年度最佳视频游戏得分</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《反叛月亮》</em>是导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zack-snyder">扎克·施奈德即将上映的科幻电影，</a>预计于 2023 年 12 月 22 日在 Netflix 上上映，目前正在准备在院线限量上映。</p><p>该<a href="https://evilgeniusgames.com/netflix-lawsuit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">诉讼</a>于今日（9 月 28 日）向加利福尼亚州中区美国地方法院提起，指控 Evil Genius Games 和 Netflix 同意发行该游戏以配合电影的上映日期。</p><p>据推测，该协议是在今年 3 月签署的，开发商向流媒体服务商支付了该电影的许可费用。利润将由双方分享，Evil Genius Games 声称其将重点从其他企业转移到桌面角色扮演游戏上。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="叛逆的月亮 |官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_rHLOXbFZtI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “除了<em>《叛逆月球》</em>主题续集、电视节目、图画小说和其他潜在内容和商品外，斯奈德先生还明确要求推出一款基于<em>《叛逆月球》</em>的 TTRPG，”诉讼中写道。</p><p> “对于 Snyder 先生来说，TTRPG 对于整个<em>Rebel Moon</em>宇宙的发展至关重要，因为它将为未来的<em>Rebel Moon</em>衍生品提供内容。”</p><p>为此，Evil Genius Games显然为游戏开发了一本228页的世界圣经、一本430页的玩家指南和一本337页的游戏大师指南。</p><p>然而，Netflix 指责开发商“违反了协议的保密条款——‘以及 Netflix 的信任’——据称在一次贸易展上发布了<em>《Rebel Moon》的</em>机密内容，然后向零售商披露了未经批准的<em>《Rebel Moon》</em>游戏的艺术作品”。</p><p>它于 2023 年 5 月终止了协议，并以此宣称拥有 Evil Genius Games 的知识产权。然而，诉讼称，两名 Netflix 员工在贸易展上向零售商展示了开发商最初推销的样本艺术品。 </p><figure id="attachment_3486798" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3486798" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3486798" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Rebel-Moon-main.jpg" alt="叛逆月亮" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Rebel-Moon-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Rebel-Moon-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Rebel-Moon-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Rebel-Moon-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Rebel-Moon-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Rebel-Moon-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3486798" class="wp-caption-text"> “叛逆的月亮”。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p> Evil Genius Games 正在寻求陪审团审判，指控其违反合同、违反善意和公平交易的默示契约、不当得利和宣告性救济。</p><p>当<em>NME</em>联系 Netflix 时，Netflix 拒绝置评。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，Meta 的新聊天机器人之一是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/snoop-dogg-is-now-a-dungeon-master-thanks-to-metas-new-ai-3505961">充当地下城主的</a>AI <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/developer-of-cancelled-rebel-moon-game-sues-netflix-3506051">被取消的《Rebel Moon》游戏开发商起诉 Netflix 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
