r /> <strong>‘减一’</strong><br /> <strong>《七人寻找十人》</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;听&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“她不会做什么”</strong><br /> <strong>《十九罪》</strong><br /> <strong>‘2006’</strong><br /> <strong>“膝盖抬起”</strong></p><p>早在一月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-reytons-land-first-number-one-album-with-whats-rock-and-roll-3388305">The Reytons 凭借他们的第二张全长专辑“What&#39;s Rock And Roll？”获得了他们的第一张英国冠军专辑。</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-reytons-on-their-bid-for-number-one-we-came-here-as-massive-underdogs-3386786">耶雷尔在榜单公布前接受了<em>《NME》的</em>采访</a>。 “我们很自豪我们能够独立完成这件事，这只是提醒您可以做到，”他解释道。 “因为多年来我们被太多的门拒之门外，我们不得不寻找不同的解决办法，让事情按照我们自己的方式发生。”</p><p> This Saturday (September 30), <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-reytons-announce-huge-homecoming-show-at-sheffield-arena-3334651">The Reytons will play a huge hometown at the Utilita Arena in Sheffield</a> as part of <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-reytons-announce-biggest-ever-uk-tour-3421172">their biggest UK tour to date</a> . You can see the full schedule below, and <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/the-reytons-tickets/artist/5296042?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=TUeRTURCWxyNT8CXSVXWIUg%3AUkFRPF2PiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">find any remaining tickets here</a> .</p><p> <strong>SEPTEMBER<br /> 30 – Utilita Arena, Sheffield</strong></p><p> <strong>OCTOBER</strong><br /> <strong>6 – O2 City Hall, Newcastle</strong><br /> <strong>7 – O2 Academy, Glasgow</strong><br /> <strong>13 – O2 Forum Kentish Town, London</strong><br /> <strong>14 – O2 Victoria Warehouse, Manchester</strong><br /> <strong>19 – O2 Academy, Bristol</strong><br /> <strong>20 – O2 Academy, Oxford</strong><br /> <strong>21 – Guild Hall, Portsmouth</strong><br /> <strong>26 – UEA, Norwich</strong><br /> <strong>27 – O2 Academy, Birmingham</strong><br 